    .when
      h2 When?
      p
        | <strong>The next class begins on January 14th, 2014.</strong> The intensive course will run 12 weeks, through April 11. Our schedule is set up like a typical 5-day work-week, with lecture in the morning and lab time in the afternoon. Friday is an open lab day where students can work with the instructor to catch up on projects or get a head start on the weekend's homework. 
